name: Reimu
desc: The Hakurei shrine maiden. Her main job is to exterminate youkai, which makes her quite moody.

name: Marisa
desc: A human magician living in the forest. Friendly and curious, but also a thief and a hoarder.

name: Kasen
desc: A hermit from the mountain. She acts as a mentor to Reimu and often lectures her. Holds a secret below her wisdom.

name: Remilia
desc: The owner of the SDM. She acts refined, but is actually quite childish. Her status makes her feared by many.

name: Aunn
desc: A komainu statue who came to life. She is pure-hearted and dutifully guards temples and shrines.

name: Tokiko
desc: A bird youkai who mostly minds her own business. Likes reading.

name: Letty
desc: A yuki-onna who is only active during the winter. Has a chill and calm demeanour, but doesn't really understand humans.

name: Rumia
desc: The youkai of darkness. Eats humans, but doesn't bother hunting them. Not the brightest.

name: Kokoro
desc: A menreiki who loves to perform Noh. She is very emotional and expresses herself through her masks.

name: Suika
desc: An oni who squats in Hakurei Shrine. Her physical strength is almost unmatched.

name: Rinnosuke
desc: The owner of Kourindou, a curio shop. Tries to be a purveyor of interesting curios, but often falls short in analysis.

name: Kosuzu
desc: The shopgirl who oversees the shop "Suzunaan". She has a relatively unhealthy obsession with youma scrolls.

name: Wriggle
desc: An insect youkai who is a leader of bugs in Gensokyo. She gets mad when you badmouth them.

name: Mystia
desc: A night sparrow who loves to sing. Also runs an izakaya and scams people using night blindness.

name: Sunny
desc: One of the three Fairies of Light. She is confident and acts as their leader.

name: Luna
desc: One of the three Fairies of Light. Calmer than other fairies, but also very clumsy.

name: Star
desc: One of the three Fairies of Light. Often lets the other two do all the work.

name: Cirno
desc: An ice fairy living on Misty Lake. Stronger than other fairies, so she’s quite full of herself.

name: Daiyousei
desc: A fairy friend of Cirno’s. Playful and mischievous, but a bit shyer than other fairies.

name: Seiran
desc: A deserter from the Lunar Capital. She seems to love her new home on Earth. Makes a mean mochi.

name: Seiran
desc: A deserter from the Lunar Capital. She seems to love her new home on Earth. Makes a mean mochi.

name: Ringo
desc: A deserter from the Lunar Capital. Gains strength from eating dango, but she also owns a dango stand.

name: Ringo
desc: A deserter from the Lunar Capital. Gains strength from eating dango, but she also owns a dango stand.

name: Tewi
desc: The White Rabbit of Inaba. Insanely lucky and known to spread luck blessings around.

name: Tewi
desc: The White Rabbit of Inaba. Insanely lucky and known to spread luck blessings around.

name: Miki
desc: A gallavanting human who is backed by immense faith in an Arthurian legends.

name: Konami
desc: A lazy youkai who likes to take long walks down the canal with her friends.

name: Kabin
desc: A firebrand amateur incident solver. She hasn't solved any incidents.

name: Yae
desc: A deceptive kitsune who enjoys playing pranks on her fellow youkai.

name: Amane
desc: A youkai who got herself trapped under a pile of scrap metal that she now lugs around as armor.

name: Tomomi
desc: A marauding youkai who pretends to be a raider along the Human Village canals. Mostly just a nuisance.

name: Yuna
desc: A hunter from the Human Village who is relatively adept at a bow, but still angers youkai when she hits them with strays.

name: Yuika
desc: A graverobbing youkai who is on the lam for her crimes in various cemetaries. Her greatest fear is running into the Yamaxanadu.

name: Miu
desc: A fledging swordswoman who wanders around, challenging fairies. It is said that she is an urban legend amongst the fairies at Misty Lake.

name: Akane
desc: A youkai nun hailing from Myouren Temple who follows her vows very loosely. Mostly there for the free food.

name: Akane
desc: A youkai nun hailing from Myouren Temple who follows her vows very loosely. Mostly there for the free food.

name: Kana
desc: A yamawaro mercenary who has been lost in the Bamboo Forest for a week.

name: Forde
desc: A cavalier from Renais. He is skilled, but reckless. He’s Franz’s brother.

name: Kyle
desc: A steadfast and honourable cavalier in sworn service to Renais.

name: Orson
desc: A cavalier of Renais. He’s a devoted husband and a serene and quiet man.

name: Tana
desc: A young lady of Frelia. She is both cheery and sociable.

name: Amelia
desc: A young girl from a small village in Grado. She is honest and sincere.

name: Innes
desc: The prince of Frelia. He’s brash and arrogant, but good at heart.

name: Gerik
desc: A mercenary leader from Jehanna. He's better known as the Desert Tiger.

name: Tethys
desc: A beautiful and charming dancer from Jehanna.

name: L'arachel
desc: A young woman from Rausten. She fights for justice and honour.

name: Dozla
desc: A berserker from Rausten. He’s a hearty man with a thirst for life.

name: Saleh
desc: A sage from the village Caer Pelyn. He’s Ewan’s solemn, but kind, teacher.

name: Ewan
desc: A sage-in-training from Jehanna. He reveres his teacher, Saleh.

name: Cormag
desc: A wyvern knight of Grado. A gentle man, but a ferocious warrior.

name: Rennac
desc: A lazy, greedy, but exceptional fighter from the Republic of Carcino.

name: Duessel
desc: A courageous general in Grado’s army. He’s better known as Obsidian.

name: O'Neill
desc: A troop leader in Grado's army.

name: Breguet
desc: Commander of a Grado military force.

name: Bone
desc: One of Bazba's henchmen.

name: Bazba
desc: The leader of Bazba's bandits.

name: Saar
desc:
Commander of Grado's border guard.
His loyalty is unshakable.

name: Rumia
desc: The youkai of darkness. Eats humans, but doesn't bother hunting them. Not the brightest.

name: Sekibanki
desc: A rokurokubi who is a member of the Grassroots Youkai Network. Usually a solitary and reclusive youkai.

name: Kagerou
desc: A werewolf who is a member of the Grassroots Youkai Network. Usually more friendly and reasonable when not acting up.

name: Wakasagihime
desc: A mermaid who is a member of the Grassroots Youkai Network. Usually keeps it on the down low when not agitated.
